#Next.js Hello World
Welcome to my first **Next.js**project! This simple "Hello World" app showcases the basics of **React** with ** server-side**rendering (SSR)** using Next.js.
##Features
-lightweight and fast server-side rendering.
-Dynamic routing with 'pages'
-Easy-to-deploy and scalable setup
##Project Structure
this project contains:
- 'pages/':All Application routes.
- 'public/':Static files like images.
- 'styles/'Custom CSS for the project
  ##Getting Started
  ### Clone the repository:
  git clone
  https://github.com/shahla1122/nextjs-hello-world.git cd nextjs-hello-world
  ### Install dependencies:
  npm install
  ### Run the development server:
  npm run dev
  ##Technologies Used
  -
  [Next.js](https://nextjs.org/)
  -
  [React](https://reactjs.org/)
  -
  [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/)
  Feel free to contribute or leave feedback! 
